{"tid":1607611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［熄燈幕後兇手］加咗習近平全家入制裁名單未？","createTime":"2019-10-01T01:57:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T04:45:23.000Z","uid":70786,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"071b45af10beaf9d3429bfc75f108192c5708391","tid":1607611,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:57:19.000Z","msg":"成個支那網軍都係聽佢指揮，當年佢都講過互聯網係國家最大隱患。<br />\n<br />\n連登仔女被習近平搞到熄燈流離失所冇網上，點解仲未有人將矛頭指向幕後策劃人？<br />\n<br />\n最後同大家分享下魯迅先生講過乜野<br />\n「中國人的性情是總喜歡調和折中的，譬如你說，這屋子太暗，須在這裏開一個窗，大家一定不允許的。但如果你主張拆掉屋頂他們就來調和，願意開窗了。」<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;《無聲的中國》一九二七年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/BHE778lCQAAaQ74.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FBHE778lCQAAaQ74.png&h=1c4e0e18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十月一賀佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d68af3b7ccb888abd435d3be06ec2b78e8c76b","tid":1607611,"uid":54303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:58:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/iamchinese2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fiamchinese2&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7Cddey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=399cfd6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/iamchinese2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有個channel專起支那人底，佢地搵到個今次負責指揮既國安高層<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ae5447190d9c0d1d13022ad00fe38567c093d5","tid":1607611,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:59:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">六區開花，去議員辦事處賀佢老母啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再</span></strong></span>企起街上面<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>圍警局</strong></span></span>，分區活動就應該<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>打游擊戰去搵該區既建制派議員</strong></span></span>同佢地開party一齊賀一賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，至於邊一區去邊間就大家自己衡量下喇﹗<br />\n<br />\n屯門區區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7Cddey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=9f0bb8b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n荃灣區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7Cddey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=6ac29085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n沙田區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7Cddey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=ecd9607b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n黃大仙區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7Cddey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=68e9d8c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n深水埗區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7Cddey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=91f94be8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n灣仔區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7Cddey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=2f18ba20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話（呢個係每日都可以做既）</span></span></strong><br />\n打電話搵議員(之前有巴打post過出黎，可以自己搵下)問下國慶期間區內有咩最新活動、巴士路線、有咩醫生診所好介紹呀等等，電話打唔通既whatsapp都可以，無whatsapp既巴絲打可以send email去，連email都無既可以fax過去查詢下，無人應既話可以搵下無限fax大法fax到佢應機為止。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2.連儂牆</strong></span></span><br />\n都係搵立法會議員/區議員辦事處啦，無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3.裝修</strong></span></span><br />\n有好多議員都扎根起屋邨做左好耐，裡面啲裝修又殘又舊，有心既手足可以襯國慶幫佢地補下油、翻新下添置返少少國慶節日既氣氛，用咩色就自己決定啦。<br />\n補充:好多office既出入口好窄，大家入office查詢既時候動作唔好太大呀，唔小心撞到佢地d玻璃就大鑊喇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>4.餵office既龜龜食野(蟲系魔法師出動)</strong></span></span><br />\n巴絲打們都可以準備少少紅蟲、蚯蚓、生雞蛋、甜野呀個d比入面既龜龜食，可以吸引到更多蟲蟲輕易大量繁殖既就更好。大家知啦，議員們公事繁忙，萬一無時間餵佢地，龜龜都仲有少少野食丫嘛。<br />\n補充：拉開櫃桶餵既時候記住小心啲，唔好倒瀉手上罐可樂呀，會惹到成地蟻架！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>原post:</strong></span><br />\n國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a>"},{"pid":"1df6dcde3b23e9bb7a70a29874be63f9fa463a8f","tid":1607611,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:00:03.000Z","msg":"聽日一戰，睇到呢個手勢就向前衝 打返轉頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1607145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1607145</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1f9510e3e7cf7b60719f85dc22b778690018af8f","tid":1607611,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:00:12.000Z","msg":"習近平：全面準確貫徹一國兩制、港人治港、高度自治<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483491-20191001.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483491-20191001.htm&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7Cddey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=23be6b9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483491-20191001.htm&h=3a34d180\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483491-20191001.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n失蹤咗咁耐嘅「港人治港、高度自治」突然又由佢口中提出嚟<br />\n唔知點解呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9770e95afe0c2015e479909478e9ef0266cc40cc","tid":1607611,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:01:55.000Z","msg":"美國只會捉d中上遊份子<br />\n你捉元首迫人地舉國反撃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804627b7a7c72116a3242c1ac8abf59060433f0c","tid":1607611,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:02:09.000Z","msg":"依家林鄭月娥係配合緊中央演緊一場叫「港人治港、高度自治」嘅戲<br />\n但林鄭對話已經踢爆咗係個大話<br />\n想向國際社會扮「港人治港、高度自治」？<br />\n收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8357174aa9f3ba535fca1c02131a7c96cfc647b","tid":1607611,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9770e95afe0c2015e4